title: TRANSFORM_TO_CAR
content:
0x2A69FFD1B42BFF9E0xD8B90941// TransformToCar
void TRANSFORM_TO_CAR(Vehicle vehicle, BOOL instantly);Parameters:vehicle: A vehicle handle.instantly: If true, the vehicle will be instantly transformed, when false the transform animation plays normally.Transforms the stormberg to its "road vehicle" variant. If the vehicle is already in that state then the vehicle transformation audio will still play, but the vehicle won't change at all.Old name:  _TRANSFORM_STORMBERG_TO_ROAD_VEHICLEOld name:  _TRANSFORM_SUBMARINE_TO_VEHICLE
